                        <interp inst="t18680127-name-139" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN KILCOY</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">Policeman</hi>). On 3rd January I took the prisoner; I asked him where he got the coin from—he said, "From a gentleman in the street"—I asked where he lived—he said, 16, Charlotte Street, Shore<lb></lb>ditch, but afterwards gave his address at a coffee-shop in Holywell Lane, Shoreditch.</p>
